name: Designer Inspired Baroque Sunnies
description: These vintage style sunnies make a great addition to any outfit!

name: Tree Spiked iPhone Case
description:
You will receive 1 tree spiked iPhone case, color of your choice.  The case is a TPU rubber case and comes with 26 brass tree spikes.  

The 2nd image is the colors avaliable for 4/4s and the 3rd image is the colors avaliable for the 5.

PLEASE NOTE that colors may vary from screen to screen.

name: MK iPhone 4/4s or 5 Case
description:
One MK iPhone 4/4s or 5 case. You will receive one case color of your choice with a gold mirror MK logo. The colors available for the 4/4s are black, white, peach, purple, mint, light pink, cream, and blue (image #2). The colors available for the 5 are black, white, blue, hot pink, red, mint, cream, and lime green (image #3).

PLEASE NOTE you will not receive a dust plug with your case.

name: Dripping LV iPhone 4/4s or 5 Case
description:
One LV iPhone 4/4s or 5 case. You will receive one case color of your choice with a gold mirror LV logo. The colors available for the 4/4s are black, white, peach, purple, mint, light pink, cream, and blue (image #2). The colors available for the 5 are black, white, blue, hot pink, red, mint, cream, and lime green (image #3). 

PLEASE NOTE you will not receive a dust plug with your case.

name: Dripping CC iPhone 4/4s or 5 Case
description:
One of a kind and hard to find.  This Dripping CC case is a hard plastic case with a gold or silver dripping CC made of laser cut acrylic.

The CC's are special made and shipped from Greece!!

The color choices for iPhone 4/4s are black, white, peach, purple, mint, pink, cream or blue (image 2).  The color choices for iPhone 5 are black, white, blue, pink, red, mint, cream, or lime green (image 3).

name: Lion Head iPhone 4/4s and 5 Case
description: One of a kind custom color of your choice lion head case.  The color options for 4/4s are white, black, cream, purple, blue, mint, peach, and pink.  The color options for the 5 are white, black, cream, blue, mint, lime green, pink, and red.

name: Gold Cross iPhone 4/4s or 5 Case
description:
You will receive one plexiglass gold mirror cross case, color of your choice.  The colors available for the 4/4s are black, white, peach, purple, mint, light pink, cream, and blue (image #2). The colors available for the 5 are black, white, blue, hot pink, red, mint, cream, and lime green (image #3).

PLEASE NOTE you will not receive a dust plug with your case.

name: Large Teddy Bear iPhone 4/4s and 5 Case
description:
Adorable and fun teddy bear case.  

You chose the color of bear and case to create a one of a kind case!!

The color choices for the bear are black, white and pink.  The bear measure approximately 74mmx46mm.  The color choices for iPhone 4/4s are black, white, peach, purple, mint, pink, cream, or blue (image 3).  The color choices for iPhone 5 are black, white, blue, pink, red, mint, cream, or lime green (image 3).

name: Jaguar Head iPhone 4/4s and 5 Case
description: One of a kind custom color of your choice jaguar head case.  The color options for the 4/4s are black, white, cream, purple, blue, mint, peach, and pink.  The color options for the 5 are black, white, cream, blue, mint, lime green, pink, and red.

name: Chunky Hint Curb Chain Necklace
description:
You will receive one (1) chunky hint curb chain necklace.  The alumininum links measure about .75" wide and 1" in length per link or roughly 19mm x 25mm. The acrylic links measure 17mm x 23mm.
The necklace measures about 18" long and has a lobster clasp closure.

PLEASE NOTE the tortoise links are slightly larger then the other colors.

name: Chunky Split Curb Chain Necklace
description: You will receive one (1), color of your choice split chunky curb chain necklace.  The alumininum links measure about .75" wide and 1" in length per link or roughly 19mm x 25mm, and the black links measure 31mm x 26mm. The necklace is roughly about 22" long and has a lobster clasp closure.

name: Acrylic Curb Chain Bracelet
description:

and the bracelet measures about 7.5" long with a 1.5" extender and lobster clasp closure. 

PLEASE NOTE the tortoise links are slightly larger in size.
